deployment.message:
Clean up deployment docs and finalize Cloudflare Pages setup
- Removed temporary troubleshooting files - Created single DEPLOYMENT.md with working configuration - Project now uses CLI deployment via wrangler pages deploy - Carl AI fully integrated and configured - Custom domain: deeptrace.projectcivitas.com
deployment.statusText: Deployment has been stopped due to SCM container restart. The restart can happen due to a management operation on site. Do not perform a management operation and a deployment operation in quick succession. Adding a small delay can help avoid any conflicts.
